headline: Nvidia's Earnings Could Make Or Break Momentum ETFs
summary: A sudden tumble in the high-flying factor names could be paving the way for a reversal, say Goldman Sachs traders, putting the spotlight on ETFs tied to the factor ahead of NVIDIA Corp.’s (NASDAQ:NVDA) closely followed earnings next week. Nvidia's quarterly results could decide the fate of momentum stocks and the ETFs that track them, after a two-week slide put the high-flying trade under pressure. Nvidia is down more than 4% in the past week. Track its prices live, here. Goldman’s High Beta Mom
